{"tid":2401640,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【我又有問題】老友泥足深陷，應該點幫？","createTime":"2021-02-10T01:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T08:35:50.000Z","uid":308853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4d7474f6be23dd3e5ef678adcf0d6eafb0e0e8","tid":2401640,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"我做咗標題黨，泥足深陷嘅唔係我老友。我只係想問吓大家，如果有個朋友或家人好似呢位朋友一樣，而家對一隻股票或衍生工具，沉晒船，每個月花錢好似課金，課到借財仔，無力還，但執迷不悟。 <br />\n<br />\n站喺佢嘅角度，佢開心，搵到女神，女神又眷顧佢，佢做人有咗意義，有寄托。 <br />\n<br />\n你叫佢唔好俾人呃啦，佢話冇俾人呃。現實世界佢搵唔到女友（你睇佢個樣），佢真係獲得滿足。 <br />\n<br />\n甚至佢幻想將來。會結出果實，幸福美滿。 <br />\n<br />\n好比有人覺得呢隻股票或者買牛熊，將會幸福美滿，佢深信呢點。我駁佢，但唔能夠否認可能有奇蹟。又睇佢繼續沉淪，仲將靚相擺上網，義無反顧。 <br />\n<br />\n你話我應唔應該阻止佢？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoGV8AL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoGV8AL.png&h=72e39e43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"036d0c6808a248539015ba302fe5233de2a1b092","tid":2401640,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"我唔係講宅男。不過兩個case相似。就係柒頭沉迷虛浮希望"},{"pid":"3f903cedb86a3ad4597523e70edf91a9c9b8de19","tid":2401640,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"弱智集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d23d4dc0319376224c1f02d329108b0810b9d8","tid":2401640,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:42:34.000Z","msg":"做人最緊要開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd336008d720e35e69b31dcc52d69eba0df14cf","tid":2401640,"uid":29565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:43:37.000Z","msg":"哇 點解我而家先知有呢條出路"},{"pid":"5abf4c320c9acf4d3e9ead8b6dbd5edb90e2b931","tid":2401640,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fd336008d720e35e69b31dcc52d69eba0df14cf","tid":2401640,"uid":29565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"